# Config split into ~/.config/fish/conf.d/*.fish:
#   00-paths.fish      - environment variables and PATH
#   05-editor.fish     - EDITOR selection
#   10-aliases.fish    - aliases
#   15-functions.fish  - custom functions (ls, e, tree, ping, nr, hr, etc.)
#   20-ssh.fish        - SSH_AUTH_SOCK
#   30-interactive.fish - starship, atuin, auto-tmux, fzf opts
#   40-lm-studio.fish  - LM Studio CLI PATH
